{"tid":1310600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遇暴力藍絲等於送頭","createTime":"2019-07-12T17:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T17:50:41.000Z","uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"022baf962d5c4e104af699d911621cce0742db44","tid":1310600,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:50:41.000Z","msg":"唔打鳩佢地，都咪送頭丫～依個咪幾簡單易用囉，之前睇果D自衛術9唔搭8，覆雜過咩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;閒時同戰友練下，增強防禦力！擋到，先有得還拖啦屌～<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/guard_UIivo_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fguard_UIivo_1200x0.png&h=6ac20450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">立場新聞<br />\n「近日圍繞連儂牆爭議，多次爆發肢體衝突，常有自稱醉酒人士在各區撕走牆上紙條，早前在九龍灣連儂牆，更有市民被自稱醉漢連打十三拳。有拳館就在 FB 發片，指近日香港各區都有暴徒出沒，教市民如何保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n片段介紹用手護頭的 「High guard defense」，除了用手護頭外，亦要壓低重心移動腳步，「唔好企係度俾人打」，片段最後提醒市民要好好保護自己和身邊人，「香港加油」。」</span></span><br />\n[size=3][size=3]<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E6%8B%B3%E9%A4%A8%E7%99%BC%E7%89%87%E6%95%99%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E9%98%B2-%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92-%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E9%A0%AD%E9%83%A8%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E7%A7%BB%E5%8B%95-%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E4%BC%81%E4%BF%82%E5%BA%A6%E4%BF%BE%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%258B%25B3%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2598%25B2-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25BC%2581%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25BA%25A6